  "text": "Given the large cross-country data sample that is employed in the present paper, a financial openness measure is used that was for the first time provided by [CITATION_1] based on the IMF's Annual Report on Exchange Arrangements and Exchange Restrictions (AREAER), restrict i,t and restrict j,t . It does not account for the effectiveness of capital controls but only states whether restrictions on capital flows are in place or not.",
